summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 4143, entitled "An Ordinance authorizing the compromise and settlement of claims for delinquent assessments for street improvements, and the dismissal of suits commenced therefor, in certain cases, and providing for the manner of such compromise, settlement and dismissal, and repealing Ordinance No. 2159, approved June 16, 1892", approved April 10, 1896.
